This way I can open

14:24.149 --> 14:25.784
my secret safe...

14:25.784 --> 14:29.888
...completely undetected.

14:29.888 --> 14:32.491
Now that I've shown you
my scatting ability,

14:32.491 --> 14:35.561
I shall open the safe.

14:35.561 --> 14:37.362
She thinks she can get
inside my head.

14:37.362 --> 14:41.903
